name: TC_03_01_08 |  Verify that user can navigate through Header links Logo
description: To verify that user can navigate through Header links.
descriptionHtml: To verify that user can navigate through Header links.

testStage.description: To verify that user can navigate through Header links.

steps.name: Preconditions: Login as a registered user
Click on the Logo in Hearder.
Verify user is redirect to Logo page
Verify that Home page has "Millions of domains with the ultimate privacy protection" heading.
Verify that Home page has "Search" button.
